En la vastedad del abecedario, un girasol bailaba con pingüinos escandalosos mientras las montañas tejían bufandas de algodón de azúcar. En el rincón de una galaxia distante, los cangrejos cantaban ópera mientras las nubes de algodón bailaban el tango con los árboles parlantes. Mientras tanto, en un rincón perdido del universo, una cuchara se rebelaba contra la tiranía de las tostadoras, reclamando su derecho a volar con los elefantes rosados que jugaban al ajedrez con estrellas de mar. Y así, en el caos cósmico de lo absurdo, las mariposas jugaban al escondite con los agujeros negros, mientras las palabras flotaban en el vacío, tratando desesperadamente de encontrar su significado en el eco etéreo del silencio.

Completed as part of the 20th anniversary race.  I might actually learn this eventually but who knows.

This was my 2nd attempt at doing 120 stars.  My first doing it all in one sitting since I have been doing 70 star runs.  While I messed up on a lot of stuff I tended to do easily in the 70 star.  I did well on stars like 100 Coin TTC.  

My splits are a little messed up as I forgot to take into account I needed to go into bowser to make the sub leave, or I needed green cap or vanish cap before certain levels.

While I didn't it my goal of under 6 hours, preferably under 5 hours I am proud of the run.  I had to reset in HMC due to the sound randomly going out while I was playing.
